{
  "sourceLanguage": "en",
  "version": "1.0",
  "strings": {
    "Set up your phone": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Configurez votre téléphone"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "STEP %lld / %lld": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ÉTAPE %lld / %lld"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Install Grok Build": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Installer Grok Build"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "TethrX drives Grok Build — xAI's terminal coding agent. Install it on your computer with one command:": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "TethrX pilote Grok Build — l'agent de programmation en terminal de xAI. Installez-le sur votre ordinateur avec une seule commande :"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Already installed? Check with  grok --version  and skip ahead.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Déjà installé ? Vérifiez avec  grok --version  et passez à la suite."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Grok Build is installed": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Grok Build est installé"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sign in to Grok": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Connectez-vous à Grok"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Run Grok once on your computer. It opens your browser to sign in with your xAI account, then remembers you.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lancez Grok une fois sur votre ordinateur. Votre navigateur s'ouvre pour vous connecter avec votre compte xAI, puis il se souvient de vous."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sign-in trouble? Some privacy browsers (Brave, and others with strict shields) block the localhost redirect the login uses. Set Safari or Chrome as your default browser, run  grok login  to retry, then switch back. You're set when  grok --version  prints a version without complaints.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Problème de connexion ? Certains navigateurs privés (Brave, entre autres) bloquent la redirection localhost utilisée par la connexion. Définissez Safari ou Chrome comme navigateur par défaut, relancez avec  grok login , puis revenez en arrière. C'est bon quand  grok --version  affiche une version sans se plaindre."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "I'm signed in": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Je suis connecté"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Install Node.js": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Installer Node.js"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The bridge runs on Node.js 20 or newer. Install it from nodejs.org if you don't already have it.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le bridge fonctionne avec Node.js 20 ou plus récent. Installez-le depuis nodejs.org si vous ne l'avez pas déjà."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Should print v20 or higher.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Doit afficher v20 ou plus."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Node is installed": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Node est installé"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Start the bridge": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Démarrer le bridge"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "One command downloads and starts the bridge on your computer. It prints a pairing token and keeps running — leave it going.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Une seule commande télécharge et démarre le bridge sur votre ordinateur. Il affiche un jeton d'appairage et reste actif — laissez-le tourner."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Want it always-on? Install once with  npm i -g tethrx-bridge  then run  tethrx-bridge.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pour l'avoir en permanence : installez avec  npm i -g tethrx-bridge  puis lancez  tethrx-bridge."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The bridge is running": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le bridge est lancé"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "How will your phone reach it?": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Comment votre téléphone va-t-il s'y connecter ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pick how this phone connects to the bridge:": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Choisissez comment ce téléphone joint le bridge :"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Same Wi-Fi": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Même Wi-Fi"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "phone + computer on one network — simplest": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "téléphone + ordinateur sur le même réseau — le plus simple"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "From anywhere": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Depuis n'importe où"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "works on cellular too, via Tailscale": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "fonctionne aussi en cellulaire, via Tailscale"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Install Tailscale on your computer": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Installer Tailscale sur votre ordinateur"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tailscale is a free private network that links this phone to your computer from anywhere. Install it on your computer, then sign in to create a free account — you can use Google, Apple, GitHub, or email.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tailscale est un réseau privé gratuit qui relie ce téléphone à votre ordinateur depuis n'importe où. Installez-le sur votre ordinateur, puis connectez-vous pour créer un compte gratuit — avec Google, Apple, GitHub ou un e-mail."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Get it from the Mac App Store or tailscale.com/download. Once you're signed in, a menu-bar icon shows it's connected.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Disponible sur le Mac App Store ou tailscale.com/download. Une fois connecté, une icône dans la barre des menus confirme la connexion."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Installed and signed in": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Installé et connecté"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Install Tailscale on this phone": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Installer Tailscale sur ce téléphone"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Now install Tailscale from the App Store on this phone and sign in with the same account you just used on your computer. Using the same account on both is what links the two devices.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Installez maintenant Tailscale depuis l'App Store sur ce téléphone et connectez-vous avec le même compte que sur votre ordinateur. C'est ce compte commun qui relie les deux appareils."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Open the Tailscale app and check that both your computer and this phone show up in the list and appear connected.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ouvrez l'app Tailscale et vérifiez que votre ordinateur et ce téléphone apparaissent tous deux dans la liste, connectés."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Signed in with the same account": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Connecté avec le même compte"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Open the pairing page": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ouvrir la page d'appairage"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "On your computer, type this address into the browser's address bar:": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sur votre ordinateur, saisissez cette adresse dans la barre d'adresse du navigateur :"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Type it yourself — for your security the page refuses to open from a clicked link. It shows QR codes for Wi-Fi and Tailscale plus your token, and only works on the computer running the bridge.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Saisissez-la vous-même — par sécurité, la page refuse de s'ouvrir depuis un lien cliqué. Elle affiche les QR codes Wi-Fi et Tailscale ainsi que votre jeton, et ne fonctionne que sur l'ordinateur qui exécute le bridge."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "I see the QR codes": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Je vois les QR codes"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Scan the Tailscale code": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Scannez le code Tailscale"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Scan the Wi-Fi code": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Scannez le code Wi-Fi"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "On the pairing page, tap Scan to pair and aim at the code labelled TAILSCALE.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sur la page d'appairage, touchez Scanner pour appairer et visez le code marqué TAILSCALE."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "On the pairing page, tap Scan to pair and aim at the code labelled WI-FI / LAN.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sur la page d'appairage, touchez Scanner pour appairer et visez le code marqué WI-FI / LAN."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Scan to pair": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Scanner pour appairer"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "or enter by hand": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ou saisir à la main"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "BRIDGE ADDRESS": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ADRESSE DU BRIDGE"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "PAIRING TOKEN": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "JETON D'APPAIRAGE"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "from the pairing page": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "depuis la page d'appairage"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "CONNECT": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "SE CONNECTER"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "CONNECTING": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "CONNEXION"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "back": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "retour"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "FOUND NEARBY": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "TROUVÉS À PROXIMITÉ"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Welcome back": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Bon retour"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This phone is already paired. Reconnect to the same computer — or set it up again below.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ce téléphone est déjà appairé. Reconnectez-vous au même ordinateur — ou refaites la configuration ci-dessous."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Reconnect": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se reconnecter"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Reconnecting…": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Reconnexion…"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Try the demo": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Essayer la démo"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A client for Grok Build · independent, not affiliated with xAI": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un client pour Grok Build · indépendant, non affilié à xAI"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "That doesn't look like a TethrX pairing code.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ceci ne ressemble pas à un code d'appairage TethrX."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "WORKING DIRECTORY": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "DOSSIER DE TRAVAIL"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/Users/you/project — blank = daemon default": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "/Users/vous/projet — vide = dossier par défaut"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "New sessions run Grok in this folder. Plan mode, effort, and approvals are set inside each session.": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les nouvelles sessions lancent Grok dans ce dossier. Le mode plan, l'effort et les approbations se règlent dans chaque session."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "SESSIONS": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "SESSIONS"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "New folder": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nouveau dossier"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "New folder…": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nouveau dossier…"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "search sessions": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "rechercher des sessions"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "// no sessions yet — tap + to start": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "// aucune session — touchez + pour commencer"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "// nothing matches “%@”": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "// rien ne correspond à « %@ »"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Ungrouped": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sans dossier"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "// empty — use ••• on a session to move it here": {
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "// vide — utilisez ••• sur une session pour la déplacer ici"
          }
